       program-id. Conundrum4 as "Conundrum4".

       environment division.
       configuration section.

       data division.
       working-storage section.
       01 V    PIC 9(7) COMP.
       01 TEST-VARIABLES.
           03 A    PIC X(9).
           03 B    PIC 9(5)V99.
           03 C    PIC 9(1) COMP.
           03 D    PIC 9(7) VALUE 2000.
           03 E    PIC 9(4).
           03 F    PIC X(2).

       procedure division.
       MOVE ZEROS TO V
       DISPLAY "V=" V
       MOVE ZEROES TO TEST-VARIABLES
       display "TEST VARIABLES=" 
       display "A=" A
       display "B=" B
       display "C=" C
       display "D=" D
       display "E=" E
       display "F=" F
       DISPLAY "------------------------------"
       MOVE 1500001   TO A B
       display "A=" A
       display "B=" B
       ADD B          TO D
       ADD 1000 D .99 TO C
       MOVE C         TO E
       ADD 10000      TO E
       MOVE D         TO F
       
      
       
       display "C=" C
       display "D=" D
       display "E=" E
       display "F=" F

           goback.

       end program Conundrum4.
